    "question": [
        {
            "text": "Orbit $X$ yang mengorbit Matahari diketahui memiliki orbit elips. Bila kecepatan maksimumnya empat kali kecepatan minimumnya, berapa eksentrisitas orbit objek tersebut?"
        }
    ],
    "choices": [
        {
            "value": "0",
            "label": "0,0"
        },
        {
            "value": "1",
            "label": "0,2"
        },
        {
            "value": "2",
            "label": "0,4"
        },
        {
            "value": "3",
            "label": "0,6"
        },
        {
            "value": "4",
            "label": "0,8"
        }
    ],
    "answer": "3",
    "explanation": [
        {
            "text": "Pada elips berlaku: $v_r^2=2GM\\left(\\frac{1}{r}-\\frac{1}{2a}\\right)$."
        },
        {
            "text": "Kecepatan maksimum $v_p$ didapat ketika jarak minimum (di perihelion) sedangkan kecepatan minimum $v_a$ didapat ketika jarak maksimum (di aphelion)."
        },
        {
            "text": "\\begin{eqnarray*}"
        },
        {
            "text": "\\frac{v_p^2}{v_a^2}&=&\\frac{2GM\\left(\\frac{1}{r_p}-\\frac{1}{2a}\\right)}{2GM\\left(\\frac{1}{r_a}-\\frac{1}{2a}\\right)} = \\frac{\\left(\\frac{1}{a(1-e)}-\\frac{1}{2a}\\right)}{\\left(\\frac{1}{a(1+e)}-\\frac{1}{2a}\\right)} = \\frac{\\frac{2-1+e}{2(1-e)}}{\\frac{2-1-e}{2(1+e)}} = \\frac{(1+e)^2}{(1-e)^2} "
        },
        {
            "text": "\\frac{v_p}{v_a}&=&\\frac{(1+e)}{(1-e)} = 4 "
        },
        {
            "text": "4-4e&=&1+e "
        },
        {
            "text": "5e&=&3 "
        },
        {
            "text": "e&=&0,6"
        },
        {
            "text": "\\end{eqnarray*}"
        }
    ],
